<table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=1>
	<tr>
		<td valign=middle align=left width=22><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=1 width=20 border=0></td>
		<td valign=middle align=right class="header">Creating/Editing A Resource</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">You may add as many resouces into the system as you wish. To do so, you must have the permission that is set in the group(s) that you belong to.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Adding Resource</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the  New Resource link on the menu.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Enter the resource Name and Description.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select a category via the pull down menu or create a new category. Unused category will be automatically deleted.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">You can upload an image of the resource or link to an URL.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If booking the resource by a user requires an approval, select Yes for the option. Then, specify the approver(s) by selecting (checking) the approving user(s) from the pop up box selection and click on the Select button. To unselect, click on the name and click on the Unselect buttton.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Specify if this resouce is for Public (all users of the system) or Private (selected groups of users). To specify private usage for a group, select the group name from the Available box, click on the >> button. Click unselect, click on the group name in the Selected box and click on the << button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">7.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">For the finer private users selection, click on the User Select box. You may select (check) the users from the pop up box. Click on the Select button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">8.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To complete creating a resouce click on the Add button on the page.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Updating Resource</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Resource Listing link on the menu.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the resource name.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Edit button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Edit the setting for the resource concern.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Update button to complete.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
